==English==

===Etymology===
From [[spy]] + [[ware]] a contraction of [[software]]

===Noun===
'''spyware'''

#{{cattag2|internet|uncountable}} A [[program]] that [[monitor]]s the actions of a computer, and [[transmit]]s this data via the [[Internet]]. Spyware is [[distribute]]d by being [[bundle]]d with programs that users are likely to [[download]], and it is then [[install]]ed without the user knowing. The term spyware overlaps with adware, although spyware is considered to be more [[unethical]].

